    "en": {
      "title": "Schools are open again from Monday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided to start schools from next Monday (25th). Schools were supposed to resume from the 21st, but considering the crisis situation that has arisen due to fuel and transportation difficulties in the country, it has been decided to resume schools from Monday, 25.07.2022, the Ministry of Education said in a statement.",
        "A series of instructions have been sent to Provincial Education Secretaries, Provincial Education Directors, Zonal Education Directors, Divisional Representative/Assistant Education Directors and all principals to start and run schools, and accordingly it has been decided to carry out academic activities in all schools. It is further stated in an announcement."
      ],
